  18 Jan 2016; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> meguri-fonts-20101113a.ebuild:
  Tidy up installing document files

   - run nkf with "--overwirte" option
   - avoid installing documents to same directory

  18 Jan 2016; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> meguri-fonts-20101113a.ebuild:
  media-fonts/komatuna-fonts,meguri-fonts,mmcedar: Update SRC_URI

   Because their archives have moved from sourceforge to osdn.jp.

  18 Jan 2016; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> meguri-fonts-20101113a.ebuild:
  migu-vbd,monapo,yasashisa-{antique,gothic}: Fix license
   IPAfont license is applied to them.
  IPAfont doesn't allow dual-license and stricter than mplus-fonts.
   FYI: http://d.hatena.ne.jp/itouhiro/20120607

  01 Jan 2016; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> meguri-fonts-20101113a.ebuild:
  **/*.ebuild: Change 2015 to 2016 in the GPLv2 copyright expressions

  25 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> meguri-fonts-20101113a.ebuild:
  media-fonts/*: Add "mirror" to ${RESTRICT}

   Because they are not uploaded in GENTOO_MIRRORS.

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> meguri-fonts-20101113a.ebuild:
  Update ebuild file format from "# $Header: $" to "# $Id"

   Since Gentoo changes the VCS from CVS to git, ebuild header is changed.

  04 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> metadata.xml:
  media-fonts/*: Fix typo in metadata.xml

*meguri-fonts-20101113a (03 Jun 2015)

